title: MONDAY 5/24 - PATRIOTS INTERESTED IN JULIO JONES
itunes:title: MONDAY 5/24 - PATRIOTS INTERESTED IN JULIO JONES
description:
The Patriots are the latest team to be reported to be interested in superstar wideout Julio Jones. Pete Carroll sounds off on the Russell Wilson rumors that have dominated Seattle's offseason. Finally, Bruce Arians and Tom Brady are looking to repeat, but Arians makes it clear, his retirement plans aren't dependent on Tom Brady.
